[{"id":11,"title":"公道杯","content":"#\n\n公道杯又叫做公平杯，和一般俗称的茶海、茶盅其实是类似的东西。\n\n公道杯的作用，简单的说就是放已经泡好的茶汤，避免茶叶泡太老，产生苦涩，另外也有评比及调匀茶味的用途。\n\n泡茶时难免茶来不及喝，这时要是一直泡在茶壶，茶汤就会过浓，产生苦涩。 为了将茶汤保持在最合适、最甘甜的状态，就要在泡好时另外盛放。因此就有公道杯的产生。\n\n公道杯不仅可避免茶泡太久，也有调匀浓淡的功能。不同泡的茶叶，口感若是过浓过淡，可以加以调整，达到最适合的浓淡口感。\n\n另外公道杯可以给多个客人均分茶汤，让每位客人都品尝到相同品质的茶汤。\n\n这也是公道杯及公平杯名称的由来。","routePath":"/zh-CN/blog/gong-dao-bei","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":12,"title":"博客","content":"#\n\n * 公道杯","routePath":"/zh-CN/blog/","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":13,"title":"联系我们","content":"#\n\n * 电子邮件: gowiden@gmail.com\n * 电话: --","routePath":"/zh-CN/contact","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":15,"title":"Dragon ball (龙珠)","content":"#","routePath":"/zh-CN/tea/dragon-ball","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":16,"title":"Raw tea (生茶)","content":"#\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","routePath":"/zh-CN/tea/raw-tea","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":17,"title":"Ripe pu-erh tea (熟茶)","content":"#","routePath":"/zh-CN/tea/ripe-pu-erh-tea","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":18,"title":"White tea (白茶)","content":"#\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","routePath":"/zh-CN/tea/white-tea","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":19,"title":"Yi (易字饼)","content":"#","routePath":"/zh-CN/tea/yi","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""},{"id":20,"title":"Yuan (元字饼)","content":"#","routePath":"/zh-CN/tea/yuan","lang":"zh-CN","toc":[],"domain":"","frontmatter":{},"version":""}]